-- Goldman Sachs downgrades stocks to neutral for the short-term
-- 
-- Fri Jul 25, 2014 03:57PM EDT
-- None



July 25 (Reuters) - Goldman Sachs <GS.N> downgraded its global allocation to equities to neutral on a short-term basis on Friday, even though the brokerage remains overweight stocks for the longer term, it said in a research note.

